		<h1 class="entry-title section-title">NY Sports Betting Apps: 6 Best Mobile Sportsbook Promos</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->
	
	<div class="post-thumbnail">
	<div class="image-wrapper">
				
				<img width="1200" height="800" src="https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png?w=1200" class="crop-center wp-post-image" alt="NY Sports Betting Apps: Best Mobile Sportsbooks" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png 1200w, https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png?resize=700,467 700w, https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png?resize=768,512 768w, https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png?resize=384,256 384w, https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png?resize=900,600 900w, https://www.amny.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/New-York-sports-betting-app.png?resize=50,33 50w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" title="NY Sports Betting Apps: 6 Best Mobile Sportsbook Promos 1">			</div>
